{"word":"κακῶς","slug":"κακῶς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰαϰῶς</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κακός\">κακός</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <b>badly, ill<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> most <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in the phrase <el>ϰ. ἔχειν</el> be ill/sick <b><a href='B:470 4:24'>Mt 4:24</a>; <a href='B:470 9:12'>9:12</a>; <a href='B:480 1:34'>Mk 1:34</a>; <a href='B:490 5:31'>Lk 5:31</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κακῶς\">κακῶς</a> δαιμονίζεται</el> under the terrible power of a demon <b><a href='B:470 15:22'>Mt 15:22</a>;</b> <el>σεληνιάζεται ϰαὶ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κακῶς\">κακῶς</a> πάσχει</el> is moonstruck/lunatic and suf-fers severely <b><a href='B:470 17:15'>17:15</a>.</b> Then by <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of the moral sphere <b>in a bad way, wrongly <a href='B:500 18:23'>J 18:23</a>; <a href='B:510 23:5'>Ac 23:5</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κακόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κάκωσις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}